description:
This version (v3)&nbsp;has been updated from two previous versions after modifying the definition for Interorbital Breadth (IOB)&nbsp;and adding new images for Palate Shape (PS).&nbsp;  

 This document presents the standardized protocol for scoring cranial macromorphoscopic traits on virtual 3D renderings of subadult crania using the Amira visualization software. This protocol was developed as part of National Institute of Justice Award 2019 DU-BX-0039. 

 &nbsp;

